icking run last year, and many in the industry agree that the party is just starting. In that, we\u2019ve seen many of the more popular tech stocks now trading at nosebleed valuations. Hence, investors are looking to gain more exposure to</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1210742344/image_1210742344.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742940-poet-technologies-high-risk-high-reward-in-the-ai-data-center-revolution", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 08:42:55"}, {"id": "4742939", "title": "XPeng: Not Good Enough Yet To Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180151608/image_2180151608.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"XPeng Motors Store\" data-id=\"2180151608\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180151608/image_2180151608.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180151608/image_2180151608.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180151608/image_2180151608.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180151608/image_2180151608.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180151608/image_2180151608.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180151608/image_2180151608.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180151608/image_2180151608.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2180151608/image_2180151608.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcapti